{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f47e97e9d5","title":"对邓子恢报告中关于基本完成农村社会主义改造时间的传达问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"88ebb64234","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"f47e97e9d5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"8c378fae80","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓子恢，当时任中共中央农村工作部部长。"},{"id":"2f38a56d86","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央东北局1953年5月16日关于传达邓子恢在中央农村工作会议的总结时应注意事项给所属的电报上。"},{"id":"9d9d09aedb","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央东北局在给所属的电报中说：各地在传达邓子恢在中央农村工作会议上的总结时，对其中“十年至十五年或更多些时间在全国范围内基本上完成农村社会主义改造”一语，在中央未指示如何传达以前，只可传达到县委书记一级干部，并应啊哈他们暂不下达，亦不向群众宣传，以免引起部分群众不必要的思想混乱"}],"contents":[{"id":"c64a374702","type":"title","text":"对邓子恢报告中关于基本完成农村社会主义改造时间的传达问题的批语吗","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5"},{"id":"8c378fae80","type":"paragraph","text":"邓子恢同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5"},{"id":"2f38a56d86","type":"paragraph","text":"此事有通知各地之必要，请考虑加按语转发此电，或另拟一电，送我一阅为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5"},{"id":"9d9d09aedb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5"},{"id":"46556eb977","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5"}],"page":{"id":"9547463a34","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"f47e97e9d5